<div id="review_1260905746" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1260905746" />
    <a title="Denise Liebig" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/35981467-denise-liebig"><img alt="Denise Liebig" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1413667441p2/35981467.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1260905746?book_show_action=true">Apr 21, 2015</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Denise Liebig" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Denise Liebig" href="/user/show/35981467-denise-liebig">Denise Liebig</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1260905746" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer8661284940878559434">I received a copy of “From Afar” in exchange for an honest review, and I was pleasantly surprised by how much I enjoyed it. Morgan Stanfield’s often emotional journey, later set in vivid detail in the streets of St. Petersburg, Russia, quickly captured my attention. And Mr. Scozzari’s wit and sarcasm had me laughing out loud. It was a quick, fun and thoroughly entertaining read. I highly recommend it!</span>

          </span>
        </div>


